---
title: British-Inspired Shrimp Pie with Cheesy Mash and Peas
description: Cousin to shepherd's pie, this British-inspired fish pie is a comforting, creamy stew studded with shrimp and veggies and topped with a quilt of cheesy mashed potatoes.
